You pulverize the caramel in your spice grinder?  That must take a while, since spice grinders are small.  I just throw it in the food processor.  How crunchy is your butter?  Mine resembles natural-style peanut butter.  At home, you can&#8217;t get it as smooth as commercial Nutella, because they use very strong nut grinders.</p>
		
